{"tid":1047532,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞和街後巷雜物遭縱火 警追緝縱火狂徒","createTime":"2019-03-05T04:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T12:20:52.000Z","uid":7439,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"276c438655cce3d6fc62a420d7b444ddf8539168","tid":1047532,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T04:23:59.000Z","msg":"觀塘瑞和街與瑞寧街交界發生火警。今日(3日)凌晨零時許，放置於上址後巷的一堆雜物起火，一時間火光熊熊，適時有司機駕駛的士在附近等客，見狀報警。消防員到場開喉，迅即將火救熄，發現約5乘5米範圍內的雜物焚毀，火警中無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n消防經調查後，相信該堆雜物由附近的拾荒者檢獲後擺放該處，認為火警原因有可疑，案件暫列縱火，交由觀塘區刑事調查隊跟進，並翻查現場天眼片段，追緝涉案狂徒，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190303/photo/bkn-20190303010258234-0303_00822_001_04b.jpg?20190304042809\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190303%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190303010258234-0303_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20190304042809&h=84105744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190303/photo/bkn-20190303010258234-0303_00822_001_02b.jpg?20190304042809\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190303%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190303010258234-0303_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20190304042809&h=342d0514&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7c9b3df864e8e0c9971f9474832938892c18c02","tid":1047532,"uid":47783,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T05:01:12.000Z","msg":"發現約<span style=\"color: red;\">5乘5</span>米範圍內的雜物焚毀，火警中無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n5&times;5=25&rarr;肉酸<br />\n肉酸rip \\|/"},{"pid":"ea71f32c8d5a0ad6560304876845d584b35a39f5","tid":1047532,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T05:02:18.000Z","msg":"罪惡之街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c2993890507cca7709a0422e10946ac3c72f2c","tid":1047532,"uid":122167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T05:03:21.000Z","msg":"港版哥譚市"},{"pid":"ab56eaa205e2e378683a97296dee341dc8afbde1","tid":1047532,"u